messages.message:
Hey team, wanted to share a quick :relaxed: highlight from a customer (Kering) regarding their experience building apps in AI Hub. This came up earlier today during a research session focused on deployments and how Instabase fits into the broader customer workflow—beyond upstream and downstream integrations.

Check out the clip from *23:35 to 23:51* in the recording below, and feel free to watch more if you have time.

> “Well, it's pretty great, because it's very user-friendly and I'm not having any problem developing apps on Instabase.”
Recording link: https://instabase.zoom.us/rec/share/tquNShC5GPJEVzS0muyH2ApTnQO9lhYdU4bIMxSRp9kz_0G6WCJOlGfjN1mmlek.0SDiD3B6lnvLhwHt
